Comment: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------text-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在这晴朗的星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搭着日向的父亲去工作时的顺风车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,正在前往群马的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,您今天要做什么采访呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算写山田升先生的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,山田先生是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他征服了好几个8000米的高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是群马出身的伟大登山家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,书写好了请务必让我拜读
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我说老爸 从这能看到谷川岳么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要离开高速公路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,呿～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天前往的是回忆之峰·谷川岳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,…才怪 是城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,位于群马的岩石主题公园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,LockHeart城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,枫姐要和优佳姐开学习会 没能一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但住在群马的洸会跟我们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,洸——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正楷体_GBK\c&H00E97D50\3c&H00FFFFFF\i1\b1\fs60\bord4\pos(640,396.429)}『拍下回忆吧！』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我傍晚时再来接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我也是刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,搭巴士来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让大哥送我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个LockHeart城 我早就想来看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是心奈酱提议来这里的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说这是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听说城堡是从苏格兰一整个搬过来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可今天也是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以蛮期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大城堡～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会有公主呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,青蛙先生真可爱{\c&H7A7BFF&}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,河马先生和松鼠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就连狮子先生也有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,力量石？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是摸了感情就会丰富起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,使你一直专情下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写着要两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给情侣干的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感受到自己的情感澎湃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真假啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,葵姐没有感受到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是好像有点丰富起来 又好像没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快救救人家呀 葵——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人家到底做了啥要遭此罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,日向姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,别管她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}救～救～偶～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上去前 先吃午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 肚子饿得扁扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好馋人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开动啦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这咖喱可真豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是老爸玩BINGO中的送给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没拍出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那个只要等一下照片就会浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是那样么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我也带了相机哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我能给大家拍张照吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,OK♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 要拍喽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来 茄子～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拍得怎么样 给我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是用的胶卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,胶卷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟数码相机不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,胶卷的得拿去洗照片才知道有没有拍好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那还挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,并不会 这正是乐趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,由于有张数限制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因此每一张都很宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天要拍很多能留下回忆的照片哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00B2AFFA\3c&H008878DD\fn方正粗圆_GBK\frz18.57\fs55\pos(249.6,121)\bord3\b1}手机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是爱心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为叫LockHeart吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是那样么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,葵你也爬上来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别强人所难啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我说有才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,…还真有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她们好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,公主体验
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好的♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,洸姐也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,锵锵～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好咧 来拍照吧♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们再靠近一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,更近一点啦{\c&H7A7BFF&}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 茄子～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里挺暗的 不用开闪光拍么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我这相机用的是明亮的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,开放值是F2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,F2？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种阴暗环境下也能用正常的快门速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要特地提高感光度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,JPEG和RAW两个格式我都保存了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,之后再调整曝光和色彩平衡也行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拍得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怎么拍人 稍微试试后还蛮有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这次换我来给洸姐你拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,安啦安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,难得成了公主嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,洸 快笑一个笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,洸姐 拍人物有什么窍门吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,窍门？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是在对方开始显得生硬前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,自然地拍下去…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看到什么UFO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拍到很棒的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上你的当了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,UFO 在哪里 哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得拍下来 必须！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,先不管UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拍了许多照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在LockHeart城中渡过了十分充实的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这趟来得值了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢心奈酱推荐了一个这么棒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,洸 怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,日向的父亲还没到么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才发讯息给我 应该差不多要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也没怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,洸 久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,洸的哥哥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好轻浮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,洸受你们照顾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,您这车好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹你看得出来么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,前不久才到手到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以声音才这么炫酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,减震器也超赞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 大哥你就别说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 洸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,平常不都是「葛格谢谢你来接我{\c&H7A7BFF&}❤{\c&HFFFFFF&}」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样撒娇的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱说啊笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你这家伙在害羞么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,洸令人意外的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢 你快消停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那 下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,照片之后发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待哟♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么啦 这么傲娇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,胶卷全都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到家后把照片都洗出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然在手机上和电脑上看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种触手可及的照片也别有一番韵味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们留下了许多开心的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不知洸是否也这么觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H005D5F60\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\b1\frz356\t(0,2000,\fs51)\move(625.6,506.6,622.4,524.2)}日向 心奈 葵 洸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,待续
